sql:
SELECT 
  d.Document_Object_ID, 
  COALESCE(COUNT(r.Related_Document_Object_ID), 0) AS related_documents_count
FROM 
  Document_Objects d
LEFT JOIN 
  Document_Subset_Members r ON d.Document_Object_ID = r.Document_Object_ID
GROUP BY 
  d.Document_Object_ID
ORDER BY 
  related_documents_count ASC
LIMIT 1;

sql:
SELECT d.Document_Object_ID, COALESCE(COUNT(dsm.Related_Document_Object_ID), 0) AS related_count
FROM Document_Objects d
LEFT JOIN Document_Subset_Members dsm ON d.Document_Object_ID = dsm.Document_Object_ID
GROUP BY d.Document_Object_ID
ORDER BY related_count ASC
LIMIT 1;
